prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, a whimsical and funny watercolor illustration featuring the couple from the reference photo, ID 7a820487-1150-4634-827d-7ceb0003a40c. The scene is a chaotic kitchen. Lao Lao, on the left, is laughing hysterically, pointing at Jordan who is on the right. Jordan, looking comically dismayed and covered in flour and pink frosting, is holding a lopsided, slightly burnt birthday cake with crooked candles. Flour dust puffs are in the air, and frosting splatters are on the counter and his face. Their outfits are consistent with the photo: Lao Lao in a light blue sweatshirt and Jordan in a tan hoodie. The background is a simple, charming kitchen rendered in soft, blended watercolor washes of pale yellow and mint green. The style is lighthearted and sketchy with flowing colors and soft edges, creating a charming, humorous atmosphere. In the center of the card, below the main action, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable, dark brown handwritten cursive script. Flat 2D artwork, bright and cheerful color palette.
